OL,3,CHow do tsunami warning systems work?
OL,5,FThey can hit any coast at any time.
OL,6,FBut they can't be prevented, and for
OL,7,Fpeople living in coastal communities,
OL,8,Fall they can do is prepare for if, or
OL,9,Fwhen, one happens.
OL,11,FThe only respite is that tsunamis
OL,12,Fdon't occur often, and the majority
OL,13,Fare not destructive.
OL,15,FWhat is a Tsunami?
OL,17,FThe word Tsunami is Japanese, coming
OL,18,Ffrom the characters for harbour
OL,19,F("tsu") and wave ("nami").
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/13
