OL,3,CHow do tsunami warning systems work?
OL,5,FA tsunami is a series of extremely
OL,6,Flong waves, primarily caused by
OL,7,Funderwater earthquakes, which suddenly
OL,8,Fdisplace the ocean's floor.
OL,10,FOther possible causes are landslides,
OL,11,Fvolcanic activity, certain types of
OL,12,Fweather, and meteorites.
OL,14,FLike a rock that is dropped in a
OL,15,Fpuddle - tsunamis radiate outwards in
OL,16,Fall directions from the point of
OL,17,Forigin.
