OL,3,CHow do tsunami warning systems work?
OL,5,FTsunami waves can move as fast as a
OL,6,Fjet plane, clocking in at over 500
OL,7,Fmph. Some have enough power to cross
OL,8,Fentire ocean basins.
OL,10,FIf looking at the water's surface
OL,11,Fwhile far out at sea, tsunamis can go
OL,12,Fundetected. Boats may not normally
OL,13,Fnotice one as it passes below them.
OL,15,FAs the waves reach shallow water near
OL,16,Fland, they slow down and grow in
OL,17,Fheight - most tsunamis are less than
OL,18,F10 feet high, but some can reach over
OL,19,F100 feet.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/13
