OL,15,FThe History of Tsunami Warning Systems
OL,17,FThe creation of large-scale tsunami
OL,18,Fwarning systems began in the 1940s,
OL,19,Fformed separately by Japan and the US
OL,20,Fafter both experienced destructive
OL,21,Ftsunamis.
