OL,3,CHow do tsunami warning systems work?
OL,5,FThe Ring of Fire is an area laden with
OL,6,Fvolcanoes and sites of seismic
OL,7,Factivity, covering the edges of the
OL,8,FPacific Ocean.
OL,10,FAn estimated 75% of all active
OL,11,Fvolcanoes are dotted along the Ring of
OL,12,FFire, and 90% of all earthquakes occur
OL,13,Fthere.
OL,15,FUnesco says 76% of history's fatal
OL,16,Ftsunamis have occurred in the Pacific
OL,17,FOcean.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/13
