OL,3,CHow do tsunami warning systems work?
OL,5,FHowever, the Indian Ocean Tsunami, or
OL,6,Fthe Boxing Day Tsunami, which killed
OL,7,F230,000 people, highlighted the need
OL,8,Ffor tsunami warning systems elsewhere
OL,9,Fand changed the way they work.
OL,11,FThe ITV News team reflect on their
OL,12,Fexperiences of reporting on the Boxing
OL,13,FDay Tsunami, which struck in 2004.
OL,15,FHow do Tsunami Warning Systems Work?
OL,17,FThe first sign of a potential tsunami
OL,18,Fis usually an earthquake, which
OL,19,Fcreates seismic waves.
