OL,3,CHow do tsunami warning systems work?
OL,5,FIf the earthquake meets certain
OL,6,Fcriteria, warning centres use
OL,7,Finformation from water-level networks.
OL,9,FThese monitor changes in the water
OL,10,Fusing sea-floor censors and surface
OL,11,Fbuoys, which can indicate the
OL,12,Fexistence and size of a tsunami.
OL,14,FTsunami warning centres will run
OL,15,Fforecast models to simulate the
OL,16,Ftsunami's movements across the ocean
OL,17,Fand estimate its predisposition for
OL,18,Fdamage, such as wave height, arrival
OL,19,Ftimes, location and duration.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/13
