OL,3,CHow do tsunami warning systems work?
OL,5,FThese forecasts allow warning centres
OL,6,Fto decide if a tsunami alert should be
OL,7,Fupdated or cancelled.
OL,9,FThe system is not foolproof, though.
OL,11,FIf a tsunami is triggered by a non-
OL,12,Fseismic event, like a volcanic
OL,13,Feruption or meteorite, water-level
OL,14,Fnetworks may not be able to create a
OL,15,Fdetailed forecast with enough time,
OL,16,Fand seismic networks won't pick it up
OL,17,Faccurately.
OL,19,FWhat Types of Tsunami Alerts are there?
