OL,3,CHow do tsunami warning systems work?
OL,5,FThere are three levels to tsunami
OL,6,Falerts: a tsunami watch, a tsunami
OL,7,Fadvisory, and a tsunami warning.
OL,9,FA tsunami watch is issued when a
OL,10,Ftsunami may later impact the watch
OL,11,Farea. It can be upgraded or cancelled
OL,12,Fdepending on updated information.
OL,14,FA tsunami advisory is issued when a
OL,15,Fpotentially dangerous tsunami is
OL,16,Fimminent, expected or occurring.
OL,17,FSevere flooding is not expected in
OL,18,Fareas under an advisory, but local
OL,19,Fofficials may evacuate immediate
OL,20,Fcoastal areas like beaches, harbours
OL,21,Fand piers.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/13
