OL,3,CHow do tsunami warning systems work?
OL,5,FA tsunami warning is issued when a
OL,6,Ftsunami with the potential to cause
OL,7,Fwidespread flooding is imminent,
OL,8,Fexpected or occurring, which could be
OL,9,Faccompanied by powerful currents and
OL,10,Fcontinue for several hours. Officials
OL,11,Fmay evacuate low-lying coastal areas
OL,12,Fand reposition ships to deep waters if
OL,13,Fthere is time.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/13
